      "value": "<p><span style=\"font-family:Signika\">This adversary wields the power of Typhoon Release, which makes wind release even more devastating. When this adversary casts a jutsu with the Wind Release keyword, double the range and increase any area of effect by 10ft.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:Signika\">This adversary can also always choose which creatures are affected by Wind Release jutsu, and can cast Wind Release jutsu with Dexterity.</span></p>",
